thread.title: Dom
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Dom

author: Dom
title: Dom
text:
Rented a Toyota Corolla from Omega Nelson NZ early Feb 2017 for 5 days. Everything was great, friendly helpful service (even picking us up from our accommodation to collect the car & dropping us back at airport terminal after hire) car was in very good condition & we had absolutely no problems at all.
Great experience all round!
